[[Spanish|The Spanish Wikibook]] was created on August 2, 2003 by [[User:ThomasStrohmann|ThomasStrohmann]]; it was the first language book on Wikibooks. During December 2006, it underwent a complete archive and rewrite, by [[User:Celestianpower|Celestianpower]]. A list of major contributors &mdash; past and present &mdash; can be found below.
* {{user|ThomasStrohmann}}
* {{user|Karl Wick}}
* {{user|Wintermute}}
* {{user|Mariela Riva}}
* {{user|Mxn}}
* {{user|Sabbut}}
* {{user|Javier Carro}}
